# Testing

## Vitest

- Unit tests: `test/unit/`
- Nuxt component tests: `test/nuxt/`
- Use `@nuxt/test-utils` for Vue components

## Playwright

- E2E: `tests/*.spec.ts`
- Config: `playwright.config.ts`

## Running

```bash
pnpm test          # Vitest
pnpm test:e2e      # Playwright
pnpm test:coverage # Vitest with coverage
```
